# Credit Card Approval Prediction using Machine Learning

---

# Project Documentation

## Project Title

Credit Card Approval Prediction using Machine Learning

---

# Abstract

Credit card approval is an important decision-making process for banks and financial institutions. Manual verification of thousands of applications every day is time-consuming and prone to human errors. This project uses Machine Learning algorithms to automate the approval process by predicting whether a customer's credit card application should be approved or rejected based on historical applicant information.

The system provides quick, consistent, and accurate predictions through a user-friendly Flask web application.

---

# Problem Statement

Financial institutions receive a large number of credit card applications daily. Evaluating each application manually increases operational costs and processing time. Human decisions may also introduce inconsistency.

This project aims to build an intelligent prediction system that automates the approval process using Machine Learning techniques.

